And since her contract had ended, it was legally ambiguous.

461
00:29:06,285 --> 00:29:07,285
Contract ended?

462
00:29:07,725 --> 00:29:08,754
Yes. Her contract...

463
00:29:08,755 --> 00:29:10,624
