500
00:31:16,885 --> 00:31:18,725
Woof woof, happy now?

501
00:31:20,755 --> 00:31:21,755
You crazy jerk.

502
00:31:22,755 --> 00:31:24,594
So, Ji An did...

503
00:31:24,595 --> 00:31:26,465
