515
00:31:56,255 --> 00:31:58,725
So, when they get angry, they can't form structured sentences...

516
00:32:00,825 --> 00:32:01,895
What? What's the problem?

517
00:32:02,665 --> 00:32:05,094
As a friend, not a therapist,

518
00:32:05,095 --> 00:32:06,935
