519
00:32:08,265 --> 00:32:10,705
- Okay. - Yes.

520
00:32:12,175 --> 00:32:14,074
So, when people get angry,

521
00:32:14,075 --> 00:32:15,175
they just blurt out words randomly.

522
00:32:15,845 --> 00:32:16,845
They say this and that.

523
00:32:16,875 --> 00:32:17,875
Sometimes they repeat...

524
00:32:17,876 --> 00:32:19,015
